WEBVTT

01:39.370 --> 01:43.590
[Road to Success]

01:44.690 --> 01:47.920
[Episode 21]

02:01.840 --> 02:02.480
Five of characters.

02:02.480 --> 02:04.000
There's something fishy
between you two.

02:04.000 --> 02:06.310
-We're just in sync.
-Hurry.

02:09.030 --> 02:11.000
I'm in such good luck today.

02:11.000 --> 02:11.630
Watch it.

02:12.840 --> 02:13.360
Pung!

02:14.870 --> 02:16.360
-Good for you.
-I just won.

02:16.360 --> 02:17.710
And you won big.

02:17.710 --> 02:19.630
-You’re so lucky.
-Take a bite.

02:19.630 --> 02:21.430
Can't believe you pulled it off.

02:26.630 --> 02:27.560
You're back?

02:29.800 --> 02:30.740
Leave him be.

02:31.000 --> 02:32.110
Pay up!

02:36.280 --> 02:37.540
Chengye, you're back.

02:37.560 --> 02:39.000
Your mom and the others already ate.

02:39.000 --> 02:40.030
I saved some food for you.

02:40.030 --> 02:41.120
Come eat it in a bit.

02:41.280 --> 02:42.110
Auntie.

02:43.910 --> 02:44.840
That thing...

02:45.280 --> 02:46.740
Is it a gift from him again?

03:18.960 --> 03:21.680
Finally, a big weight's off my mind.

03:22.150 --> 03:22.750
Ms. Lin,

03:22.750 --> 03:25.680
you're not letting things
take their own course now?

03:25.680 --> 03:27.150
If I keep on that track,

03:27.150 --> 03:30.030
I'll be stuck in a rut
and achieve nothing.

03:32.240 --> 03:34.440
You took the words right out of my mouth.

03:35.870 --> 03:37.680
What do you mean, Coach Wang?

03:40.960 --> 03:43.750
We're back on good terms now, aren't we?

03:46.240 --> 03:47.800
Yes, merely.

03:48.190 --> 03:49.120
We have merely

03:49.120 --> 03:51.240
restored our partnership

03:51.240 --> 03:52.910
maintained by mutual interests.

03:52.910 --> 03:53.800
Is that all?

03:54.400 --> 03:55.960
What else do you want?

04:00.150 --> 04:00.680
I...

04:07.870 --> 04:09.030
There's a flower shop ahead.

04:09.030 --> 04:10.960
I'm going there to buy fertilizer.

04:11.210 --> 04:13.010
♪ Every night ♪

04:11.430 --> 04:12.310
I...

04:13.760 --> 04:15.870
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

04:16.630 --> 04:18.540
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

04:19.029 --> 04:21.720
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

04:22.410 --> 04:23.470
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

05:14.190 --> 05:15.480
I know. I know.

05:17.720 --> 05:19.270
Do you dare to hit me?

05:21.630 --> 05:24.560
-Coach, Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

05:25.040 --> 05:27.000
We just heard from
the organizing committee

05:27.000 --> 05:29.590
that our next opponent has been changed
to Yongchuan Hengjiu.

05:29.590 --> 05:30.740
Yongchuan Hengjiu?

05:30.760 --> 05:32.360
Are you kidding me?

05:32.390 --> 05:34.010
Weren't we supposed to play Xinpeng?

05:34.010 --> 05:36.090
The students of Xinpeng
were informed on a short notice

05:36.090 --> 05:38.390
of attending an important local event
that overlaps

05:38.390 --> 05:39.650
in schedule with the match.

05:39.650 --> 05:41.730
As if we weren't already on thin ice.

05:42.390 --> 05:43.790
What was that gibberish?

05:44.290 --> 05:45.210
Ms. Lin,

05:45.750 --> 05:47.750
they can't just change our opponent,
can they?

05:47.750 --> 05:49.350
In the group round-robin,

05:49.370 --> 05:51.870
it's reasonable and compliant
with the rules to adjust the sequence

05:51.870 --> 05:52.720
of group matches.

05:52.720 --> 05:53.920
But that doesn't mean
they had to replace

05:53.920 --> 05:55.750
our original opponent
with Yongchuan Hengjiu.

05:55.750 --> 05:58.300
They scored nine goals
in their previous match.

05:58.300 --> 05:59.250
Nine goals.

05:59.950 --> 06:01.380
Their list of players includes

06:01.380 --> 06:03.270
three National Youth Team members.

06:03.270 --> 06:04.620
One of them is Fang Sulun,

06:04.620 --> 06:06.710
who did a bicycle kick in the box
in an earlier match

06:06.710 --> 06:08.710
against the Japanese Youth League,

06:09.050 --> 06:10.580
showcasing superb skills.

06:10.800 --> 06:12.230
Not to mention Qin Qiechu.

06:12.230 --> 06:13.410
Everyone on the online forum

06:13.410 --> 06:14.970
says he's being groomed

06:14.990 --> 06:16.570
as a key reserve player
for the national team.

06:16.570 --> 06:17.450
Wait.

06:17.560 --> 06:18.560
Do you have to throw a wet blanket

06:18.560 --> 06:19.950
on everyone at a time like this?

06:19.950 --> 06:21.480
I'm just stating the facts.

06:22.070 --> 06:23.220
Fragility is not to be denied.

06:23.220 --> 06:24.510
Enough, the two of you.

06:28.650 --> 06:29.560
Coach.

06:29.590 --> 06:30.790
What's your opinion?

06:31.390 --> 06:32.720
What opinion can I have?

06:32.730 --> 06:34.790
You all did a good job on the analysis.

06:34.800 --> 06:36.530
I was not asking you about that.

06:36.750 --> 06:39.680
I meant our chances
of defeating Yongchuan Hengjiu.

06:43.630 --> 06:44.830
The chances are slim,

06:45.190 --> 06:46.520
but there is still hope.

06:46.800 --> 06:48.800
I think you should just
eat and sleep well,

06:48.800 --> 06:50.930
and get onto the field with a calm mind.

06:56.510 --> 06:57.830
Go home and rest early.

06:57.830 --> 06:58.730
Conserve your energy.

06:58.730 --> 07:00.660
Try your best in tomorrow's match.

07:00.830 --> 07:01.750
Okay.

07:04.950 --> 07:06.800
Can't believe we'll play Hengjiu.

07:06.800 --> 07:07.920
This is so stressful.

07:07.920 --> 07:08.870
Bye bye.

07:08.870 --> 07:09.680
Just take the coach's advice.

07:09.680 --> 07:10.940
Eat and drink as usual.

07:11.950 --> 07:14.240
I probably won't be able to sleep tonight.

07:14.240 --> 07:16.300
You make it sound like you could do it.

07:16.560 --> 07:18.430
Off you go. We'll walk together next time.

07:18.430 --> 07:19.310
Okay, I'm leaving then.

07:19.310 --> 07:20.510
-Bye.
-I'm leaving too. Bye.

07:20.510 --> 07:21.480
-Bye.
-Bye bye.

07:21.680 --> 07:22.680
Goodbye, Ms. Lin.

07:23.310 --> 07:24.510
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

07:24.950 --> 07:26.310
Goodbye, Coach.

07:27.740 --> 07:28.690
Fu, shall we?

07:28.710 --> 07:29.270
Sure.

07:34.670 --> 07:35.600
Anything wrong?

07:42.220 --> 07:43.480
Did you lose anything?

07:43.870 --> 07:45.310
I can't find my keychain.

07:45.870 --> 07:48.400
The one with that utterly ugly jersey,
right?

07:48.430 --> 07:49.750
If it's gone, just let it be.

07:49.750 --> 07:51.750
That stuff's tacky after all, right?

07:51.750 --> 07:52.750
Fu Xinshu!

07:54.120 --> 07:57.190
-Fu Xinshu, look what time it is now.
-No, I must find it.

07:57.190 --> 07:58.310
I'll buy you a new one tomorrow.

07:58.310 --> 07:59.360
Let's go grab a bite first.

07:59.360 --> 08:00.680
Come on. Let's go.

08:37.440 --> 08:38.630
Hey, kids.

08:38.630 --> 08:40.530
Let's go watch cartoons.

08:40.549 --> 08:41.600
Come on, kids.

08:44.790 --> 08:47.320
Kids, time to watch cartoons.

08:47.320 --> 08:48.320
Hey, kiddo?

08:51.390 --> 08:52.640
Everyone's here, right?

08:52.640 --> 08:54.520
Yiling, come on.

09:03.360 --> 09:06.090
Why didn't you go watch cartoons
with the others?

09:06.820 --> 09:08.250
I don't know them.

09:08.280 --> 09:10.140
Don't you want to get to know them?

09:11.120 --> 09:11.960
I've seen you staying

09:11.960 --> 09:13.270
in your ward alone several times.

09:13.270 --> 09:14.600
Where are your parents?

09:15.240 --> 09:16.790
They didn't come see me.

09:19.030 --> 09:20.240
Do you play football?

09:21.060 --> 09:23.050
I just joined the school team
this semester.

09:23.050 --> 09:24.500
Let's go play football together.

09:24.500 --> 09:26.150
But we're in a hospital now.

09:26.170 --> 09:27.230
It doesn't matter.

09:27.400 --> 09:29.040
I have a big secret hideout.

09:32.240 --> 09:32.720
Come with me.

09:32.720 --> 09:34.380
Don't keep yourself in the ward
all the time.

09:34.380 --> 09:35.360
Basking in the sun outside

09:35.360 --> 09:37.620
more often will help you recover faster.

09:37.910 --> 09:38.790
My name is Fu Xinshu.

09:38.790 --> 09:39.790
What's yours?

09:42.410 --> 09:43.970
My dad doesn't like me.

09:43.990 --> 09:45.510
And I hate being his son.

09:45.910 --> 09:47.240
So I don't have a name.

09:53.000 --> 09:54.690
I'll call you Bed No. 4 then.

09:56.730 --> 09:58.590
Let's go play football, Bed No. 4.

10:02.310 --> 10:03.790
Quick!

10:06.550 --> 10:07.680
I'll go get the ball.

10:12.800 --> 10:13.930
Bed No. 4,

10:13.970 --> 10:15.000
today, I'll teach you how to

10:15.000 --> 10:16.390
precisely get hold of the ball.

10:16.390 --> 10:17.240
Okay.

10:17.960 --> 10:18.790
Bed No. 4.

10:18.260 --> 10:21.150
♪ Who hasn't known
the dark of night and uncertainty? ♪

10:19.030 --> 10:19.790
You stay right here.

10:19.790 --> 10:20.480
You're still in recovery.

10:19.910 --> 10:20.990
[Dangerous zone; Do not climb]

10:20.480 --> 10:21.240
Do be careful.

10:21.240 --> 10:21.720
Got it.

10:22.100 --> 10:25.290
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

10:24.150 --> 10:24.910
Very good.

10:26.110 --> 10:31.570
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

10:30.900 --> 10:32.150
[Dangerous zone; Do not climb]

10:34.390 --> 10:37.250
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

10:38.460 --> 10:41.660
♪ Looking up,
dreaming side by side of great ideals ♪

10:42.560 --> 10:48.310
♪ The vast world
awaits youth to arrive ♪

10:47.840 --> 10:50.870
Fu Xinshu, this is no fun at all.

10:49.230 --> 10:51.880
♪ If facing every storm is ♪

10:50.870 --> 10:51.840
Let's both take a few steps back.

10:51.840 --> 10:53.360
You should kick harder.

10:52.990 --> 10:55.690
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

10:55.150 --> 10:56.320
Over here.

10:56.320 --> 10:57.120
Catch it.

10:57.080 --> 10:59.310
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

10:58.550 --> 10:59.550
Now, pass it to me.

10:59.600 --> 11:00.030
Okay.

11:00.620 --> 11:02.930
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

11:02.440 --> 11:04.040
Catch this one. Here it goes!

11:04.330 --> 11:07.180
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

11:08.550 --> 11:10.900
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

11:12.580 --> 11:13.540
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

11:14.570 --> 11:15.790
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

11:17.070 --> 11:19.110
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

11:19.160 --> 11:24.250
[Fu Xinshu] [Bed No. 4]

11:20.270 --> 11:23.070
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

11:23.600 --> 11:24.480
Come on, pass it over!

11:24.220 --> 11:26.370
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

11:25.080 --> 11:25.510
There it goes.

11:25.510 --> 11:26.360
Okay!

11:26.630 --> 11:28.200
P-Pass the ball to me.

11:28.140 --> 11:29.710
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

11:29.480 --> 11:30.360
Pass it now!

11:30.670 --> 11:31.810
♪ Thrive and bloom ♪

11:32.680 --> 11:35.620
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

11:36.540 --> 11:39.440
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

11:36.910 --> 11:38.070
Pass the ball!

11:39.120 --> 11:40.600
You've got this! Shoot!

11:57.870 --> 11:58.720
Bed No. 4.

11:59.700 --> 12:01.630
You'll be discharged soon, right?

12:11.870 --> 12:14.980
Fu Xinshu, thanks for teaching me
how to play football.

12:18.840 --> 12:19.480
It looks cute.

12:19.480 --> 12:21.010
I'll hang it on my backpack.

12:22.080 --> 12:23.840
Then you must never take it off.

12:24.760 --> 12:25.910
Bed No. 4,

12:26.080 --> 12:27.320
you're about to leave the hospital,

12:27.320 --> 12:29.120
yet I still don't know your name.

12:31.280 --> 12:32.950
Well, then meet me next week

12:33.030 --> 12:35.510
on my birthday
at that fried chicken place.

12:35.750 --> 12:37.720
I'll tell you when you get there.

12:37.720 --> 12:38.840
Okay. I'll definitely be there.

12:38.840 --> 12:39.440
Great.

12:39.750 --> 12:40.360
Come on.

12:40.360 --> 12:41.960
-Pinky swear.
-Pinky swear.

12:41.960 --> 12:43.840
-No backsies.
-No backsies.

12:56.480 --> 12:57.870
I promised a classmate

12:58.030 --> 12:59.910
to spend my birthday with him.

12:59.910 --> 13:00.840
No, you can't go.

13:01.790 --> 13:02.960
You have to spend this birthday

13:02.960 --> 13:04.360
with your grandparents.

13:05.240 --> 13:07.040
We are moving to Yongchuan soon.

13:07.080 --> 13:08.320
Why are we moving?

13:08.320 --> 13:10.480
To start a new company—
at least it appears so.

13:10.480 --> 13:11.480
But in fact,

13:11.480 --> 13:12.360
it's just to make it easier

13:12.360 --> 13:13.960
for your dad to meet with his side piece.

13:13.960 --> 13:14.750
Hu Yongping!

13:15.050 --> 13:18.180
Why did you have to speak nonsense
when our son's around?

13:18.410 --> 13:19.270
What did I do wrong?

13:19.270 --> 13:20.440
Spare me that crap.

13:20.440 --> 13:21.770
You want to dump me, huh?

13:21.790 --> 13:23.080
I'm telling you, not a chance.

13:23.080 --> 13:24.120
Shut that filthy mouth of yours!

13:24.120 --> 13:24.960
I want to go to...

13:24.960 --> 13:25.840
You shut it too!

13:25.840 --> 13:26.480
Listen up, sign the papers

13:26.480 --> 13:27.200
if you want a divorce.

13:27.200 --> 13:27.720
Why can't I speak?

13:27.720 --> 13:28.510
Retain what little shame you have.

13:28.510 --> 13:29.910
-You may have it, but I still do!
-I'm not going to divorce you.

13:29.910 --> 13:30.870
-Chengye!
-You stay put!

13:30.870 --> 13:31.600
Chengye!

13:32.320 --> 13:33.360
Where are you going?

13:33.360 --> 13:34.200
Chengye!

13:34.840 --> 13:35.720
Chengye!

13:36.320 --> 13:37.720
Come back here, Chengye!

13:39.480 --> 13:40.320
Chengye!

13:41.000 --> 13:42.130
Chengye, come back!

13:44.390 --> 13:46.650
Never ever come back if you dare run away!

13:54.360 --> 13:55.600
You should've watched out.

13:55.600 --> 13:56.390
Little boy,

13:56.390 --> 13:57.120
are you okay?

13:57.120 --> 13:57.870
I'm fine.

14:20.340 --> 14:24.660
[Available all day on workdays]
[Breakfast deals]

14:22.840 --> 14:24.100
Thank God I'm not late.

14:55.600 --> 14:57.550
Come on, get some fries.

14:57.910 --> 14:59.080
What a spread.

14:59.080 --> 15:01.080
Help yourself to whatever you like.

15:08.910 --> 15:10.500
Has he forgotten our pact?

15:10.530 --> 15:11.960
How is it? Is it good?

15:11.960 --> 15:12.670
Yes.

15:15.680 --> 15:16.930
No vacant tables.

15:17.030 --> 15:17.890
Go ask that boy.

15:19.960 --> 15:20.670
Hey, little one,

15:20.670 --> 15:22.390
can we swap seats with you?

15:23.000 --> 15:23.980
Sure.

15:24.000 --> 15:25.110
-Thank you.
-Thanks.

15:25.110 --> 15:25.910
Thank you.

15:27.310 --> 15:28.600
What would you like to eat?

15:28.600 --> 15:30.580
What about you two?

15:36.150 --> 15:37.840
Here comes the birthday cake!

15:38.750 --> 15:40.600
Happy birthday!

15:42.240 --> 15:45.670
Happy birthday to you.

15:45.670 --> 15:48.790
Happy birthday to you.

15:48.820 --> 15:52.000
Happy birthday to you.

15:52.000 --> 15:54.440
Bed No. 4, you're about to leave
the hospital,

15:54.440 --> 15:56.000
yet I still don't know your name.

15:56.000 --> 15:57.530
Well, then meet me next week

15:57.560 --> 16:00.130
on my birthday
at that fried chicken place.

16:00.360 --> 16:02.320
I'll tell you when you get there.

16:02.320 --> 16:03.720
Okay, I will definitely be there.

16:03.720 --> 16:07.030
-Pinky swear. No backsies.
-Pinky swear. No backsies.

16:07.030 --> 16:09.000
Hello, it's our child's birthday today.

16:09.000 --> 16:11.200
We'd like to offer you a cup of ice cream.

16:11.790 --> 16:12.240
Hey, little one,

16:12.240 --> 16:13.720
a free cup of ice cream for you.

16:13.720 --> 16:16.200
-Thank you.
-Here you are, a spoon.

16:16.670 --> 16:17.720
It's our child's birthday.

16:17.720 --> 16:19.960
-We'd like to share the joy with you.
-Thanks.

16:19.960 --> 16:22.000
Look, here's ice cream.

16:24.080 --> 16:25.360
Come on.

16:25.360 --> 16:27.840
-Here you are.
-You got one yet?

16:29.550 --> 16:31.080
Are you having fun?

16:31.080 --> 16:32.200
Are you having fun?

16:33.440 --> 16:34.300
A spoon for you.

16:36.010 --> 16:43.310
[KFC]

16:41.300 --> 16:44.270
Little boy, you've been sitting here alone
the entire day.

16:44.270 --> 16:45.600
Where are your parents?

16:47.440 --> 16:48.840
We're closing the place.

16:55.790 --> 16:59.330
[KFC]

17:28.180 --> 17:30.440
Never ever come back if you dare run away!

18:41.120 --> 18:42.220
Now you get it.

18:42.880 --> 18:44.070
You're nothing

18:45.790 --> 18:47.270
when you're out of the Wen family.

18:47.270 --> 18:48.470
Finish it and go home.

18:50.880 --> 18:53.410
If you're not eating it,
put it away and get up!

19:09.620 --> 19:11.880
Wen Chengye, how come you're still here?

19:18.200 --> 19:19.400
Why did you come back?

19:19.400 --> 19:20.420
Don't get me started.

19:20.420 --> 19:22.130
I lost something really important.

19:22.130 --> 19:23.480
I must find it back.

19:32.270 --> 19:33.370
So you found it?

19:33.680 --> 19:34.930
Thank you.

19:36.610 --> 19:38.330
Is it very important to you?

19:40.590 --> 19:41.830
I made someone a promise

19:41.830 --> 19:43.290
that I'd never take it off.

19:45.950 --> 19:46.820
Why the laugh?

19:47.270 --> 19:49.400
It really is of great importance to me.

19:58.690 --> 19:59.580
Is that so?

20:03.160 --> 20:04.890
If it truly meant so much to you,

20:05.190 --> 20:06.920
how could you not recognize me?

20:10.460 --> 20:11.330
Bed No. 4...

20:13.310 --> 20:14.640
You are Bed No. 4?

20:17.830 --> 20:19.000
Drop the act.

20:19.510 --> 20:21.840
Don't pretend like you still remember me.

20:22.010 --> 20:23.000
I do remember you.

20:23.000 --> 20:24.800
How could I have forgotten? I...

20:24.920 --> 20:26.160
I've always wanted to find you

20:26.160 --> 20:28.020
and play football with you again.

20:29.640 --> 20:31.570
You were my very first best friend.

20:36.520 --> 20:38.320
Then why didn't you come meet me?

20:42.410 --> 20:43.070
We made a pinky promise

20:43.070 --> 20:45.400
that you'd celebrate my birthday with me.

20:47.000 --> 20:48.730
I waited for you for a whole day.

20:53.880 --> 20:55.200
Why?

21:03.970 --> 21:05.700
Why on earth didn't you show up?

21:18.310 --> 21:19.770
I'll ask you one last time.

21:23.680 --> 21:24.890
Why?

21:30.270 --> 21:31.470
I don't want to say it.

21:35.680 --> 21:37.080
Think whatever you want.

21:37.510 --> 21:38.970
I just don't want to say it.

21:42.140 --> 21:43.130
Fu!

21:43.470 --> 21:45.470
Wen Chengye, what's wrong with you?

21:52.070 --> 21:54.130
-You fancy a beating or what?
-Qin Ao!

22:21.070 --> 22:22.330
Come watch this video.

22:22.350 --> 22:23.270
Fu!

22:25.400 --> 22:26.510
This needle of yours

22:26.510 --> 22:28.920
is already... off track.

22:28.920 --> 22:30.250
Where is it pointing at?

22:34.640 --> 22:36.070
We could've had some more time

22:36.070 --> 22:38.330
before playing the strongest opponent.

22:39.960 --> 22:42.110
No need to look at
the points table anymore.

22:42.110 --> 22:45.070
Yongchuan Hengjiu will surely defeat
all their opponents

22:45.070 --> 22:47.130
and advance as the first in the group.

22:47.310 --> 22:50.170
But yesterday, didn't you say
there was still hope?

22:51.270 --> 22:53.010
Given our players' state now,
they might even

22:53.010 --> 22:56.470
have problems coordinating with each other
in today's match.

23:00.350 --> 23:02.550
That said, Yongchuan Hengjiu
is the strongest opponent

23:02.550 --> 23:04.350
we can meet in the current stage.

23:04.640 --> 23:07.240
Even if we lose
simply because they're better,

23:07.310 --> 23:09.920
at least our players get to
enjoy the game itself.

23:09.920 --> 23:11.270
So, why not take a positive attitude

23:11.270 --> 23:13.030
to embracing a meaningful defeat,

23:13.030 --> 23:13.680
Ms. Lin?

23:22.070 --> 23:22.930
The bus is here.

23:23.030 --> 23:23.640
Get on it, guys.

23:23.640 --> 23:25.720
-Okay.
-Coming right up.

23:25.720 --> 23:26.310
Let's go.

23:32.690 --> 23:37.240
[Youth Football Super League]

23:37.720 --> 23:39.590
Pretty fancy, isn't it?

23:41.590 --> 23:43.550
So posh.

23:43.550 --> 23:45.000
Even the stadium hosting the game
between us

23:45.000 --> 23:46.270
and Yongchuan Hengjiu is different.

23:46.270 --> 23:48.540
What a fancy lounge.

23:48.560 --> 23:49.350
I'm even more nervous now.

23:49.350 --> 23:50.590
When will the football field

23:50.590 --> 23:52.920
in our school have facilities like these?

23:53.270 --> 23:54.030
Hello, miss.

23:54.030 --> 23:55.590
My name is Qin Qiechu.

23:55.590 --> 23:56.400
Hello.

23:58.750 --> 23:59.680
Coach!

23:59.880 --> 24:00.440
Coach!

24:00.440 --> 24:01.350
Coach Winfred,

24:01.640 --> 24:02.640
I finally get to see you.

24:02.640 --> 24:04.640
I've always been a huge fan of yours.

24:04.830 --> 24:06.830
Why did you abandon our team?

24:08.350 --> 24:10.110
So, this boy is...

24:11.160 --> 24:11.680
Yes.

24:12.160 --> 24:14.160
He is Qin Qiechu from Yongchuan Hengjiu.

24:14.160 --> 24:16.070
You actually know who I am, Coach!

24:16.070 --> 24:17.310
I'm so touched.

24:18.130 --> 24:19.350
Previously, you said you'd coach our team,

24:19.350 --> 24:20.160
but you didn't.

24:20.160 --> 24:21.200
After coaching them through this match,

24:21.200 --> 24:22.460
will you join our team?

24:23.160 --> 24:23.920
Bro,

24:24.480 --> 24:26.080
don't you think you're rude,

24:26.560 --> 24:28.960
for calling another team's coach "Coach"?

24:28.960 --> 24:30.680
You're Qin Ao!

24:30.680 --> 24:32.940
I love the way you penetrate into the box!

24:33.030 --> 24:34.690
Will you give me an autograph?

24:34.920 --> 24:36.650
Just sign your name right here.

24:43.400 --> 24:44.400
Here, huh?

24:47.680 --> 24:49.270
T-To be honest,

24:49.640 --> 24:51.790
if you become a star player in the future,

24:51.790 --> 24:53.320
such handwriting won't do.

24:54.200 --> 24:55.070
A star player?

24:55.680 --> 24:56.350
Me?

25:03.200 --> 25:04.600
You're Fu Xinshu, right?

25:05.600 --> 25:07.790
You work with Chen Jianghe
in a quite interesting way.

25:07.790 --> 25:08.510
Thanks.

25:09.790 --> 25:11.160
Hello! Hello.

25:13.640 --> 25:15.840
Qi Liang! Nice to meet you.

25:15.930 --> 25:17.280
And you're Feng Suo, right?

25:17.280 --> 25:18.880
You're quite a solid player.

25:19.590 --> 25:20.480
Well...

25:20.880 --> 25:22.110
I-I have to go now,

25:22.110 --> 25:23.350
or my captain will scold me.

25:23.350 --> 25:24.670
S-See you later then.

25:25.240 --> 25:25.790
See you!

25:25.790 --> 25:26.650
See you in a bit.

25:26.880 --> 25:28.110
Bye!

25:31.160 --> 25:31.960
Guys,

25:31.960 --> 25:34.550
Qin Qiechu is quite a people person,
isn't he?

25:34.920 --> 25:36.350
He knows us so well.

25:36.350 --> 25:38.160
I have a bad feeling about it.

25:38.440 --> 25:39.310
Stop it.

25:39.310 --> 25:40.590
Keep your feelings to yourself.

25:40.590 --> 25:41.590
The game hasn't started yet.

25:41.590 --> 25:43.400
No more pessimistic talk like that.

25:43.400 --> 25:45.880
We won't know what they've got
until we fight them.

25:45.880 --> 25:46.510
That's right.

25:46.510 --> 25:48.110
Plus, the fact that our opponent

25:48.110 --> 25:49.680
takes us seriously
means we're not half bad.

25:49.680 --> 25:50.590
Exactly.

25:51.880 --> 25:53.310
Alright. It's time to get ready.

25:53.310 --> 25:54.350
Go get changed now.

25:54.350 --> 25:55.880
-Okay.
-Got it.

25:55.880 --> 25:57.550
-Let's go.
-Time to get changed.

25:57.550 --> 26:00.240
Everyone in the audience, welcome
to the Youth Super League live match.

26:00.240 --> 26:01.590
Today, the match will be held

26:00.640 --> 26:01.830
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

26:01.590 --> 26:04.590
between Yongchuan Hengjiu
and Hongjing No. 8 High School.

26:01.830 --> 26:03.780
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
versus Yongchuan Hengjiu]

26:04.880 --> 26:07.590
I believe you're all familiar
with Yongchuan Hengjiu.

26:07.590 --> 26:10.110
It's the reigning five-time champion
of the Youth Super League.

26:10.110 --> 26:12.350
Joined by star players
like No. 10, Qin Qiechu,

26:12.350 --> 26:14.920
and No. 7, Fang Sulun,
it's fair to say

26:14.920 --> 26:17.110
this team is the undisputed king
of the pitch.

26:17.110 --> 26:18.070
Most football fans

26:18.070 --> 26:19.310
believe that no one can defeat

26:19.310 --> 26:21.240
this team in the ongoing tournament.

26:21.240 --> 26:22.480
On the other hand,

26:22.480 --> 26:24.510
for their classic free-kick strategy
in the match

26:24.510 --> 26:26.270
against Yuzhou Yinxiang,
Hongjing No. 8 High School

26:26.270 --> 26:28.070
is hailed as the dark horse
of this tournament.

26:28.070 --> 26:30.960
Now, the dark horse
has stepped onto the king's territory.

26:30.960 --> 26:32.640
Who will emerge victorious?

26:32.640 --> 26:35.040
Let's see what will unfold
before our eyes.

26:35.550 --> 26:36.480
The two teams' captains

26:36.480 --> 26:37.940
are exchanging pennants.

26:40.440 --> 26:42.830
The pre-match coin toss is complete.

26:42.830 --> 26:44.640
The game is about to start.

26:45.880 --> 26:47.030
Yongchuan Hengjiu!

26:48.350 --> 26:50.210
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

26:50.440 --> 26:51.830
Hongjing No. 8 High School!

26:51.830 --> 26:54.030
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

27:13.550 --> 27:15.580
-Go for it!
-You've got this!

27:15.600 --> 27:19.070
-Go for it!
-You've got this!

27:38.480 --> 27:39.510
Right from the kickoff,

27:39.510 --> 27:42.240
Hengjiu has shown dominant control
over the pitch,

27:42.240 --> 27:44.770
and is suppressing Hongjing
in the midfield.

27:45.440 --> 27:47.200
Their 4-3-3 Formation

27:47.200 --> 27:48.590
is working pretty smoothly,

27:48.590 --> 27:50.250
with seamless coordination.

27:51.510 --> 27:54.270
Hengjiu's captain,
Player No. 7, Fang Sulun, is dribbling

27:54.270 --> 27:55.930
past the opponent's defense.

27:57.480 --> 27:58.280
Defense!

27:58.310 --> 27:59.590
-Defense!
-He sold the opposing defenders

27:59.590 --> 28:00.960
-with a feint.
-Defense!

28:00.960 --> 28:02.680
Then he passes the ball to a midfielder.

28:02.680 --> 28:03.640
The latter,

28:03.830 --> 28:04.680
without stopping the ball,

28:04.680 --> 28:06.480
passes it right back to Fang Sulun.

28:06.480 --> 28:07.960
-No. 10 bursts through the right flank.
-Qin Ao, to the right!

28:07.960 --> 28:09.490
He's about to enter the box!

28:09.720 --> 28:12.120
This kick looks like
both a pass and a shoot.

28:15.920 --> 28:18.640
Feng Suo fails to catch the ball.

28:18.640 --> 28:21.070
No. 10 comes up and shoots again.

28:22.160 --> 28:23.200
It's a goal!

28:23.400 --> 28:24.200
Qin Qiechu

28:24.440 --> 28:26.200
scored a goal
right after the game started.

28:26.200 --> 28:27.000
One to zero!

28:30.720 --> 28:33.200
Bravo! Well done!

28:39.270 --> 28:41.510
Yongchuan Hengjiu is now taking the lead.

28:41.510 --> 28:44.480
As expected of Qin Qiechu,
a star player of Hengjiu,

28:44.480 --> 28:46.610
he has put on a brilliant performance.

28:49.110 --> 28:49.960
Move!

28:56.550 --> 28:58.590
In less than five minutes
after the game started,

28:58.590 --> 29:00.640
Yongchuan Hengjiu
got a grip of the match's pace

29:00.640 --> 29:01.720
and scored the first goal.

29:01.720 --> 29:02.830
Now, for Hongjing,

29:02.830 --> 29:04.070
the priority

29:04.070 --> 29:05.110
is to steady themselves.

29:05.110 --> 29:07.510
-After all, there's still plenty of time.
-Keep your composure, guys!

29:07.510 --> 29:08.920
They still stand a chance of tying

29:08.920 --> 29:10.920
or even surpassing their opponent.

29:14.680 --> 29:17.750
Hongjing is trying to steady the pace
through passing,

29:17.750 --> 29:19.610
while seeking a chance to attack.

29:20.310 --> 29:23.640
But Hengjiu is pressing aggressively
on the pitch.

29:24.920 --> 29:26.000
Such intense pressing

29:26.000 --> 29:28.000
is giving Hongjing a very hard time.

29:30.240 --> 29:32.270
Now, the ball is with Hongjing's captain,

29:32.270 --> 29:34.640
Player No. 10, Fu Xinshu.

29:36.160 --> 29:38.310
That through ball is intercepted!

29:39.640 --> 29:40.920
They're even well aware of Fu Xinshu's

29:40.920 --> 29:41.590
passing patterns.

29:41.590 --> 29:44.050
Hengjiu disrupts the pass
and gets the ball.

29:45.030 --> 29:46.550
Now, the ball is with...

29:46.550 --> 29:48.610
Player No. 10 of Hengjiu, Qin Qiechu.

29:50.070 --> 29:51.480
With excellent skills,
he has dribbled past

29:51.480 --> 29:53.410
several opposing players in a row.

29:55.310 --> 29:57.550
Facing the defense
being put up by Hongjing,

29:57.550 --> 30:00.720
a teammate of his
quickly breaks through from the right.

30:02.510 --> 30:04.640
You want to pass the ball? Not a chance!

30:05.160 --> 30:06.160
Qin Qiechu doesn't

30:06.160 --> 30:07.590
pass the ball to the right flank,

30:07.590 --> 30:09.590
but to the midfield with a backheel.

30:10.400 --> 30:11.200
A shoot!

30:11.200 --> 30:12.600
Here comes one more goal!

30:17.830 --> 30:19.790
Good anticipation,
but we prepared two plans.

30:19.790 --> 30:20.920
Yongchuan is showing

30:20.920 --> 30:23.110
much better teamwork than Hongjing!

30:23.110 --> 30:23.880
That attack

30:23.880 --> 30:26.150
was a textbook example of teamwork.

30:26.400 --> 30:27.480
Yongchuan Hengjiu

30:27.480 --> 30:28.880
just scored another goal.

30:28.880 --> 30:31.070
Now, it's 2-0 on the field.

30:32.400 --> 30:35.400
Conceding two goal consecutively
soon after the game started

30:35.400 --> 30:36.680
might shake

30:36.680 --> 30:37.960
the mentality

30:37.960 --> 30:39.410
of Hongjing's players.

30:41.160 --> 30:42.790
Hengjiu's players are too agile.

30:42.790 --> 30:44.550
Can't believe no one on our team
fills the gap.

30:44.550 --> 30:45.790
Time is pressing.

30:45.790 --> 30:46.790
I'll do that then!

30:47.270 --> 30:48.750
Player No. 11 of Hongjing, Wen Chengye,

30:48.750 --> 30:50.830
seems to have left his position
in defense

30:50.830 --> 30:52.510
for the attacking half,
fighting for the ball.

30:52.510 --> 30:54.550
Is it a new strategy of Hongjing's?

30:54.550 --> 30:56.610
Wen Chengye left his defensive zone.

30:58.240 --> 30:58.960
Wen Chengye, what are you doing?

30:58.960 --> 31:00.350
Not only did he fail to steal the ball,

31:00.350 --> 31:02.030
but he also occupied the same position

31:02.030 --> 31:03.480
with a teammate tracking back,

31:03.480 --> 31:05.080
causing a gap in the defense.

31:05.350 --> 31:06.000
Wen Chengye,

31:06.000 --> 31:06.920
where are you going?

31:06.920 --> 31:09.070
That defensive error shouldn't have

31:09.070 --> 31:10.110
happened.

31:16.230 --> 31:16.960
Wen Chengye

31:16.960 --> 31:20.020
-is marking Qin Qiechu one-on-one again.
-Bring it on.

31:20.070 --> 31:21.680
Qin Qiechu seizes the chance

31:21.680 --> 31:22.920
to break through.

31:30.590 --> 31:32.830
He then passes the ball to his captain,
Player No. 7,

31:32.830 --> 31:34.920
Fang Sulun, who volleys hard!

31:36.920 --> 31:38.790
The ball hits a defender's leg,

31:38.790 --> 31:40.240
deflects, and finds the net!

31:40.240 --> 31:41.270
Three to zero!

32:09.720 --> 32:11.520
You alone can't turn the tables.

32:14.200 --> 32:16.030
Wen Chengye, what was that mess about?

32:16.030 --> 32:17.690
Isn't the game a mess already?

32:21.830 --> 32:23.030
Hongjing's No. 11 is a real headache.

32:23.030 --> 32:24.830
It's okay. Just try to avoid him.

32:30.350 --> 32:32.750
Yongchuan Hengjiu's passing
is rather smooth.

32:32.750 --> 32:33.830
After scoring the third goal,

32:33.830 --> 32:36.160
they've completely taken control
of the pace on the field,

32:36.160 --> 32:37.960
and are bombarding

32:37.960 --> 32:39.240
Hongjing's goal.

32:41.110 --> 32:42.830
Another link-up play in a small area.

32:42.830 --> 32:44.890
Then a long shot from outside the box.

32:49.680 --> 32:52.790
Hongjing's defense is almost collapsing.

32:52.790 --> 32:55.110
This time, a penetration
through the midfield.

32:55.110 --> 32:56.720
The ball goes to the left flank.

32:56.720 --> 32:58.720
The player gently slots it home
with his right foot.

32:58.720 --> 33:00.590
Four to zero!

33:00.590 --> 33:03.310
Yongchuan Hengjiu
extended their lead again

33:03.310 --> 33:05.310
with relentless pressing.

33:12.550 --> 33:13.810
How could this happen?

33:16.880 --> 33:18.240
This happens

33:18.240 --> 33:19.750
when all the conditions

33:20.550 --> 33:21.550
are against us.

33:41.960 --> 33:42.590
Yu Ming pulled

33:42.590 --> 33:43.720
and gave away a foul.

33:43.720 --> 33:46.640
-The referee showed him a yellow card.
-No. 5, that was a foul.

33:46.640 --> 33:49.550
Hengjiu Team gets a free kick
in the final third.

33:50.310 --> 33:51.440
-It's okay.
-Come here!

33:51.440 --> 33:52.920
-No biggie.
-Form a wall.

33:54.030 --> 33:55.430
-All is fine.
-It's okay.

34:09.440 --> 34:11.900
A free kick in a good position
around the box.

34:12.840 --> 34:14.960
Will Hongjing keep this one out?

34:14.960 --> 34:18.360
Will Hengjiu further widen the gap
by scoring one more goal?

34:20.070 --> 34:21.630
Lu, stay on him.

34:34.760 --> 34:35.510
The ball!

34:51.480 --> 34:52.630
Yongchuan Hengjiu

34:52.630 --> 34:54.030
actually adopted Hongjing's tactic

34:54.030 --> 34:55.880
on free kicks from the previous match!

34:55.880 --> 34:56.840
Player No. 19 in the offside position

34:56.840 --> 34:58.110
didn't take the ball.

34:58.110 --> 34:59.880
Instead, he let it slip through

34:59.880 --> 35:01.000
to Player No. 7, his captain,

35:01.000 --> 35:03.670
-who scored with a shot into the corner.
-Shame on them for copying our tactic.

35:03.670 --> 35:04.510
Five to zero!

35:04.510 --> 35:07.840
-It's a huge blow to Hongjing's morale.
-Put in more effort!

35:18.150 --> 35:19.960
You've got this!

35:19.960 --> 35:21.510
Run forward!

35:23.590 --> 35:24.550
Qin Ao!

35:30.550 --> 35:32.750
-There's a good chance!
-A good chance!

35:36.110 --> 35:38.000
Pass it back!

35:41.590 --> 35:42.590
-Qin Ao!
-Over here!

35:42.590 --> 35:43.480
Okay!

35:44.670 --> 35:46.400
This is a great opportunity!

35:47.150 --> 35:48.750
We can't lose one more score.

35:52.550 --> 35:53.630
We can see now

35:53.630 --> 35:55.510
Player No. 11 of Hongjing, Wen Chengye,

35:55.510 --> 35:58.710
is still pressing hard non-stop
in the middle and attacking thirds.

35:58.710 --> 36:01.710
Unfortunately, he's just running
in an extensive area

36:01.710 --> 36:04.000
without a clear target.

36:25.670 --> 36:28.150
Player No. 11 of Hongjing stole the ball

36:29.320 --> 36:31.880
by fooling Qin Qiechu with a fake.

36:31.880 --> 36:33.880
He's now dribbling the ball forward.

36:33.880 --> 36:36.670
Hengjiu is in hot pursuit of him.

36:36.670 --> 36:40.130
Both sides are battling fiercely
for the ball in the midfield.

36:44.110 --> 36:45.400
Such a shame.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.920
Player No. 11 of Hongjing fell.

36:46.920 --> 36:48.510
-Are you okay?
-Although he has outstanding skills,

36:48.510 --> 36:51.710
football requires teamwork after all.

36:51.710 --> 36:53.550
Without team support on the field,

36:53.550 --> 36:56.070
individual brilliance amounts to nothing.

37:05.320 --> 37:07.110
Wen Chengye, what are you
so arrogant about?

37:07.110 --> 37:07.840
Why put on airs?

37:07.840 --> 37:08.440
Enough, Qin Ao.

37:08.440 --> 37:10.000
I'm mad at him. What were you doing?

37:10.000 --> 37:11.320
Moving from the defensive half
to the midfield,

37:11.320 --> 37:12.630
serving as a midfielder to a forward, huh?

37:12.630 --> 37:13.920
Play or get off the pitch.

37:13.920 --> 37:14.800
Do you even know how to pass?

37:14.800 --> 37:15.800
Alright, stop it.

37:27.000 --> 37:29.000
They're having a mental breakdown.

37:30.280 --> 37:31.760
So is Wen Chengye.

37:32.190 --> 37:33.710
But at least he's clear-minded.

37:33.710 --> 37:36.070
Yes. At least he's still trying.

37:36.840 --> 37:38.320
But it won't be of help.

37:39.000 --> 37:40.070
Wen Chengye has absolutely

37:40.070 --> 37:42.670
no intention to cooperate
with his teammates,

37:42.960 --> 37:45.360
who have no idea
what he's attempting to do.

37:46.280 --> 37:47.610
What's there to do then?

37:55.000 --> 37:56.760
The first half is coming to an end.

37:56.760 --> 37:58.590
The score has reached a shocking

37:58.590 --> 37:59.260
7-0.

37:59.760 --> 38:02.030
Hongjing completely fell apart

38:02.030 --> 38:03.510
under the opponent's onslaught.

38:03.510 --> 38:05.630
This seems like the end of the first half,

38:05.630 --> 38:08.280
yet the whole game is practically over.

38:11.150 --> 38:12.230
Wen Chengye,

38:12.360 --> 38:14.090
why did you quit your position?

38:14.190 --> 38:15.280
If it weren't for you,

38:15.280 --> 38:17.360
would we have lost these many goals?

38:18.280 --> 38:19.480
What do you know?

38:20.070 --> 38:21.400
Who are you to blame me?

38:21.710 --> 38:24.320
Qin Ao, did you even see
everyone's position on the pitch?

38:24.320 --> 38:24.760
Didn't you

38:24.760 --> 38:25.710
know to run when others blocked you?

38:25.710 --> 38:27.710
You were just standing there still.

38:28.190 --> 38:29.520
Say it again, I dare you!

38:30.920 --> 38:32.710
Fine, might as well speak my mind.

38:32.710 --> 38:33.280
You guys

38:33.300 --> 38:35.650
turn into wimps
when you play against a strong team.

38:34.160 --> 38:35.500
[Youth Football Super League]

38:35.880 --> 38:37.510
You collapse at the slightest attack.

38:37.510 --> 38:38.320
What?

38:38.840 --> 38:40.760
Too embarrassed to admit
how you performed?

38:40.760 --> 38:41.070
Boss.

38:41.070 --> 38:42.900
Seems like you're not exhausted yet.

38:42.900 --> 38:43.830
[Youth Football Super League]

38:48.960 --> 38:51.280
Wen Chengye, I'm telling you,

38:51.280 --> 38:52.670
if Coach weren't here today,

38:52.670 --> 38:54.440
I would beat you up

38:54.440 --> 38:55.800
to fix that foul mouth of yours.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.330
If you want a fight so badly,

38:57.760 --> 38:59.420
let's withdraw from the game,

38:59.960 --> 39:01.960
so you can brawl till there's blood!

39:04.110 --> 39:06.510
Otherwise, save all your energy and anger

39:06.510 --> 39:07.800
for the opponent.

39:22.800 --> 39:23.960
Coach Wang is right.

39:24.480 --> 39:26.270
The first half just ended.

39:25.960 --> 39:27.720
[Youth Football Super League]

39:26.480 --> 39:28.020
The second half hasn't yet started.

39:28.020 --> 39:29.420
Everything is possible.

39:30.110 --> 39:31.310
But falling apart right now

39:31.310 --> 39:32.940
means we've already lost.

39:32.970 --> 39:33.990
Will you accept that?

39:33.990 --> 39:34.940
Of course not!

39:47.150 --> 39:49.400
Alright. Keep hydrated.

39:49.400 --> 39:50.800
Get some rest.

39:50.800 --> 39:52.060
Conserve your energy.

39:52.320 --> 39:54.780
Prepare to give it your al
in the second half.

40:02.690 --> 40:04.500
[Youth Football Super League]

40:07.710 --> 40:08.630
Wen Chengye.

40:08.120 --> 40:11.070
[Youth Football Super League]

40:09.440 --> 40:11.040
If you can't take it anymore,

40:11.480 --> 40:12.680
quit the second half.

40:12.710 --> 40:15.110
[Youth Football Super League]

40:14.510 --> 40:15.370
I'm doing fine.

40:16.630 --> 40:17.520
Wen Chengye,

40:17.930 --> 40:19.330
use this medicine spray.

40:30.470 --> 40:32.630
Taking the lead with seven scores,

40:32.630 --> 40:35.030
Hengjiu is on the pitch
for the second half.

41:02.840 --> 41:04.440
The relentless pressing in the first half

41:04.440 --> 41:05.760
has pushed Wen Chengye's stamina

41:05.760 --> 41:07.510
almost to its limit.

41:07.510 --> 41:09.150
The second half has just begun,

41:09.150 --> 41:11.400
yet he is already physically drained.

41:11.960 --> 41:14.630
-If one wants to crash and burn, let him.
-A forward of Yongchuan clearly

41:14.630 --> 41:17.110
noticed that and stole the ball from him.

41:17.110 --> 41:18.000
The physical dropoff

41:18.000 --> 41:19.360
causes Wen Chengye's technical movements

41:19.360 --> 41:21.110
to break down badly.

41:21.110 --> 41:22.670
What Wen Chengye said...

41:22.670 --> 41:23.930
Actually made a point.

41:25.670 --> 41:27.600
Their strength has improved a lot,

41:27.930 --> 41:29.320
and they have tactics in mind.

41:29.320 --> 41:31.070
But once they encounter
a super strong opponent,

41:31.070 --> 41:34.270
they lose the ability
to think quickly and analytically.

41:36.370 --> 41:38.520
We've already lost, haven't we?

41:39.710 --> 41:40.770
Do you mind it a lot?

41:41.280 --> 41:43.110
There are ups and downs in life.

41:43.400 --> 41:44.890
The same goes for a match.

41:45.150 --> 41:46.190
It's just...

41:48.110 --> 41:50.370
I'm a bit reluctant to accept the result.

41:52.670 --> 41:55.360
On the pitch,
things are constantly changing.

41:55.880 --> 41:58.480
A pre-planned formation
doesn't always work.

41:59.000 --> 42:00.070
In the face of sheer strength,

42:00.070 --> 42:01.630
all tactics are futile.

42:02.110 --> 42:04.310
Before surpassing Yongchuan Hengjiu,

42:05.030 --> 42:07.160
our players still have a long way to go.

42:07.190 --> 42:08.250
What you're saying

42:09.110 --> 42:10.990
sounds a bit fatalistic.

42:12.800 --> 42:14.060
That's not what I mean.

42:14.700 --> 42:15.630
On the contrary,

42:15.840 --> 42:17.700
I respect our players' hard work.

42:18.360 --> 42:21.590
However, football is a team sport.

42:22.150 --> 42:25.010
Now, there's already little teamwork
left in them.

42:27.030 --> 42:30.150
The players of Hongjing
are having trouble coordinating

42:30.150 --> 42:31.800
with each other
in the defensive half.

42:31.800 --> 42:34.860
The team's execution and cohesion
are both declining.

42:40.280 --> 42:42.110
Yongchuan Hengjiu
just scored another goal,

42:42.110 --> 42:44.460
extending their lead to 9-0.

42:44.670 --> 42:46.150
Hengjiu's on a great momentum,

42:46.150 --> 42:48.280
while Hongjing's defensive formation

42:48.280 --> 42:50.000
has completely fallen apart.

42:50.000 --> 42:53.660
Yongchuan Hengjiu launches
a long pass again as a counterattack.

42:54.920 --> 42:57.960
-Let me take this!
-Hongjing's No. 10, Fu Xinshu, and No. 11,

42:57.960 --> 43:00.020
Wen Chengye, sprint at the same time.

43:00.150 --> 43:01.760
The two of them collide,

43:01.760 --> 43:03.710
but neither can touch the ball!

43:06.510 --> 43:07.920
An opportunity opens for Hengjiu.

43:07.920 --> 43:09.380
They scores another goal!

43:10.590 --> 43:11.840
Bravo!

43:12.110 --> 43:12.630
Boys,

43:12.630 --> 43:13.360
good job!

43:13.360 --> 43:14.760
-Fu!
-Fu!

43:17.000 --> 43:18.550
Look, there was a foul.

43:18.550 --> 43:20.070
-Fu!
-Are you okay, Fu?

43:20.920 --> 43:23.440
-Hongjing's No. 10 appears badly injured.
-Is it the ankle?

43:23.440 --> 43:25.000
-Medics have entered the pitch.
-Fu Xinshu!

43:25.000 --> 43:26.360
They're quickly attending to the player.

43:26.360 --> 43:27.760
-Are you okay?
-The right foot, huh?

43:27.760 --> 43:28.440
My foot...

43:28.440 --> 43:29.230
Hold still.

43:29.230 --> 43:30.000
Don't move.

43:31.150 --> 43:31.590
-Qin!
-Qin Ao!

43:31.590 --> 43:33.800
-You did it on purpose, didn’t you?
-Qin Ao!

43:33.800 --> 43:34.840
Talk later. The game's still on.

43:34.840 --> 43:36.110
Qin Ao,

43:36.110 --> 43:37.170
don't be like this.

43:45.190 --> 43:46.790
Right, I did that on purpose.

43:47.070 --> 43:48.190
-So what?
-Qin Ao!

43:48.670 --> 43:49.590
Apologize,

43:49.590 --> 43:50.670
right now!

43:50.670 --> 43:51.820
You're on a football field.

43:51.820 --> 43:52.880
All of you, shut up!

43:56.200 --> 43:57.590
Coach of Hongjing,

43:57.610 --> 43:59.230
can the team captain
continue with the game?

43:59.230 --> 44:01.510
Coach, I'm feeling much better
after the ice spray.

44:01.510 --> 44:03.110
I can continue with the game.

44:03.980 --> 44:05.550
-Don't move.
-Stay still.

44:07.480 --> 44:08.230
For this match,

44:08.230 --> 44:10.230
the injured player Fu Xinshu
is leaving the field.

44:10.230 --> 44:12.690
The rest of the players
will finish the game.

44:16.070 --> 44:18.530
The rest of the players
will finish the game!

44:20.190 --> 44:21.360
Alright, let's go.

44:22.400 --> 44:23.070
Go.

44:25.760 --> 44:26.440
Be careful.

44:28.110 --> 44:28.590
Slowly.

45:15.400 --> 45:15.800
Pass it to me!

45:15.800 --> 45:17.230
After what you did to Fu,

45:17.230 --> 45:18.840
you want me to pass the ball to you now?

45:18.840 --> 45:19.960
In your dreams!

45:30.280 --> 45:31.360
Ten players against eleven.

45:31.360 --> 45:32.630
Trailing by ten goals.

45:32.630 --> 45:34.030
I've never seen a game

45:34.030 --> 45:36.440
like this in my entire career.

45:41.850 --> 45:42.960
Pass it forward!

45:43.060 --> 45:44.050
There's a window!

45:44.050 --> 45:45.100
A good chance!

45:45.230 --> 45:48.710
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
versus Yongchuan Hengjiu] [0-11]

45:45.730 --> 45:47.290
The game is over.

45:47.320 --> 45:49.840
The final score is 11-0.

45:49.860 --> 45:52.920
Yongchuan Hengjiu crushed
Hongjing No. 8 High School!

46:50.620 --> 46:51.280
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪
